All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMeetingActivity
    Activity used to create a new meeting Contains: -text fields to enter information -time picker button which opens a TimePickerDialogue -date picker button which opens up a DatePickerDialogue -spinner to select room
    AddMeetingViewModel
    ViewModel for the add meeting activity.
    DeleteViewAction
    used to perform the delete action on an item in the recycler view of the main activity.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    MainActivity
    Main activity is responsible for home page of the application.
    MainActivityViewModel
    ViewModel for the main activity.
    Meeting
    class to create meetings.
    MeetingAdapter
    Used to link the RecyclerView in the main activity with the list of meetings
    MeetingAdapter.MeetingClickListener
    Interface to handle the clicks on a recycler view item
    MeetingListTest
    Instrumental tests for the Mareu app.
    MeetingRepository
    Retrieves a fake database of meetings and rooms.
    MeetingRespositoryTest
    Unit tests for our Meeting repository
    MyDatabase
    This class is used as a fake database to provide and store data for the application It creates some pre-existing meetings in order to be able to test the application
    RecyclerViewItemCountAssertion
    Used to check if a Recycler view contains a certain amount of items
    RecyclerViewMatcher
    This class is used to find an item at a position in the recycler view in order to check the values sotred in it.
    Room
    Class used to create rooms.
    ViewModelFactory
    this class is the root of the Dependency Injection for this project.
